reviews.text:
You can ride the cars to go around Mystic Manor. That monkey touched the music box and began a scary adventure.
The effects are super cool. With shooting arrows and bombs and wind effects. Scary but interesting. Must try in Disneyland.
Not a bad ride. Could be better. Kids liked it though.

Best ride at Hong Kong Disneyland!!! It's incredibly immersive with an original storyline, amazing (anamatronic) animation, and a super cute character, Albert. I went on it several times during my visit and each time on Mystic Manor I noticed something new on the ride. It's beautifully done in its design and the decorations inside and is simply a joy to experience. Cannot recommend enough!!!

This ride is fk impressive , trackless and special effects are great. I think the star war ride in the park should adopt similar lighting special effects like mystic manor , the lighting effect is like 4D , Like they are in for air if you know what it means . Because it is trackless , your sort of wondering where the ride is going . i suggest in the last scene of the ride , where monkey king appeared breaking things apart, they should add some strong wind effect to compliment the power of monkey king .

A great ride at Disneyland Hong Kong. My 2 year old loved the lights and animatronic characters. My 5 year old was wowed by the show, and overall experience. He was just the right amount of excited, screaming, laughing and scared throughout. Adults can also enjoy the attention to detail of the ride and the drama of story. A strong recommend for people with young kids.

香港ディズニー限定の、アジアンなホーンテッドマンションとハニーハントが合わさったようなアトラクションで、絶叫が苦手な私と友達でも楽しめました！大人でも新鮮にワクワクできる仕掛けが色々あって、日本にはないディズニーの雰囲気も楽しく、何より待ち時間が少ないのも魅力です。
香港ディズニーランドは東京ディズニーランドに比べて敷地がコンパクトではあるものの、10月末でも汗だくの暑さなので暑さ対策は万全に。。ミスティックポイントはクールダウンにもちょうどいいです。近くのトリックアートが楽しめる庭園もおすすめです。
